1. *Napredujem* u učenju srpskog jezika. (I'm progressing in learning Serbian.)
2. Nadam se da će moj tim *napredovati* ove sezone. (I hope my team will make progress this season.)
3. On *napreduje* brzo u karijeri zahvaljujući svom trudu. (He is advancing rapidly in his career thanks to his efforts.)
4. Kada *napredujete* u igri, postaje sve teže. (As you progress in the game, it becomes more difficult.)
5. *Napredak* koji smo postigli u posljednjih godinu dana je izvanredan. (The progress we have made in the last year is extraordinary.)
6. Da biste *napredovali* u ovoj tvrtki, morate pokazati inicijativu i marljivost. (To advance in this company, you must show initiative and diligence.)
7. Učenje novog jezika *napreduje* polako, ali sigurno. (Learning a new language is progressing slowly but surely.)
8. Naša država *napreduje* u gospodarskom razvoju. (Our country is progressing in economic development.)